text: Billal Sebaihi (born May 31, 1992) is a French professional footballer who last played as an attacking midfielder for Kazakh club FC Caspiy. ==Career== In July 2015, he left Beira-Mar and moved to Primeira Liga club Estoril. He signed for a 3-year contract keeping him with the club till 2018 and a buyout clause of €3 million.
